French" date: "2023-06-21" categories: [markdown] --- To open this information in an interactive Colab notebook, click the Open in Colab graphic below. # Load some data ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} data(mtcars) ``` ::: # Create some plots Create a scatter plot of `mpg` vs `wt`. ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} plot(mpg ~ wt, data = mtcars, xlab = "weight (1000 lbs)", ylab = "miles per gallon") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](interactive-notebook_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-2-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: # Build a model ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} lmod <- lm(mpg ~ wt, data = mtcars) ``` ::: # Fit of model ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} plot(mpg ~ wt, data = mtcars, xlab = "weight (1000 lbs)", ylab = "miles per gallon") abline(lmod) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](interactive-notebook_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672} ::: :::
